div.div:
The second season of Yakusoku no Neverland. Fifteen children escape Grace Field House, a false paradise, hoping for a chance at freedom. Instead, they encounter plants and animals they have never before seen, and are chased by demons. The outside world is so beautiful, and yet is almost too cruel to face. Even so, the children refuse to give up. They are guided in their search for better lives only by a message from Minerva and a pen Norman left behind in order to fulfill their promise to return to the House to save those of their family who are still trapped within.
(Source: Aniplex of America) Note: Episode 1 streamed early on Amazon Prime on Jan 7, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on Jan 8, 2021.
Genjitsu Shugi Yuusha no Oukoku Saikenki

Suddenly summoned to a fantasy world and betrothed to the princess, Kazuya Souma is crowned the new king after providing the royal family with impressive advice. To rule the kingdom, he's taking the nontraditional (and very human) route of administrative reform. In a realm of dragons and elves, will this revolutionary's unique path prove effective?
(Source: Funimation)
Ikidaore mo Dekinai Konna Isekai ja
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

Sumire was a high school girl before she leapt into another world the moment she fell down. Before she could collapse and die, she came across a silver-haired boy who had already collapsed and was dying. One thing led to another and she ended up working at an Adventurer’s Guild. She doesn’t have any special powers, but she’s well liked by strange plants and animals. What does Sumire’s future hold?!
Koryuu nara Sude de Taosemasu kedo, Kore tte Joushiki janain desu ka?

Fil was raised in the mountains as the grandchild of humanity’s strongest sage, inheriting his talent for magic, and strong enough to defeat dragons with her bare hands.
However, one day, the great sage summoned Fil to tell him:
“Fil, you’re actually a girl.”
"Really!? By the way, what’s a girl?"
Fil's ignorance of gender and other common sense knowledge worried the great sage. Concerned about her future, he decided to enroll Fil into the Royal Academy. It will be the start of an exciting school life for the innocent strongest girl!
(Source: Piccoma, translated)

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
